{
  "stem": "24364.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had about, during the first months on  Mauritius, we probably had at least 50 and maybe-- possibly-- possibly 100-- I knew that-- those numbers, but I somehow I forgot them-- dead who died of typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was very many young people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I remember several of them that I was helping who died a couple of days later.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember especially one guy who was about 21 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was interesting that the Czech transport had gotten vaccination against typhoid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And nobody of us got it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So it was all the others who got typhoid fever, who were not vaccinated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So even at that time, the vaccinations apparently helped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I remember having gotten three vaccinations still in Prague before-- in Bratislava before we went on the boat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the life in the camp in general eventually became like the life in any small village or town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most people did something, like I worked in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were people who were carpenters, who worked as carpenters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there were people that were doctors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were quite a few professional.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were seamstresses.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anything you can think of was really there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Payment, of course, was minimal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Most people didn't have any money, even though eventually quite a few people got money somehow from relatives or families who were able to send them some.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the people who worked made a little bit of money, either from other camp inmates who had the money or if they worked for the camp, they were paid, again, a minimal, minimal, salary, maybe $3 a month or something like that through the camp authorities.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were people who gave lessons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were people who sold coffee, made coffee and sold coffee.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
